# Agent execution traces
# NOTE: Do not add a generic `runs/` rule here — it would greedily match the
# Next.js route directory at `frontend/src/app/(app)/runs/` and silently
# exclude the entire /runs feature from git (and therefore from Docker builds
# on the VPS, which produces 404s in production). List each trace dir
# explicitly instead.
strix_runs/
agent_runs/

